Run fast, Asfaloth. Run fast!

836
01:20:30.577 --> 01:20:34.956
What are you doing?!
Those Wraiths are still out there!

837
01:21:45.390 --> 01:21:47.390
[Noro lim, Asfaloth!]
Ride fast Asfaloth!

838
01:21:45.390 --> 01:21:47.390


839
01:22:29.571 --> 01:22:32.282
Give up the halfling, She-Elf.

840
