1207
01:55:46.351 --> 01:55:50.651
[Nai yarvaxëa rasselya...]
May your bloodstained horn...

1208
01:55:46.351 --> 01:55:50.651



1209
01:55:50.820 --> 01:55:54.720
[...taltuva ñotto-carinnar!]
fall upon enemy heads!

1210
